file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenAPI Account
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: 'http://account.lightapi.net'
paths:
  /accounts:
    get:
      summary: List all accounts
      operationId: listAccounts
      security:
        - account_auth:
            - 'account.r'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: An paged array of accounts
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Account'
              example:
                - num: 521112392
                  owner: stevehu
                  type: checking
                  firstName: Steve
                  lastName: Hu
                  sinNumber: 123456789
                  status: open
                - num: 521112321
                  owner: stevehu
                  type: investment
                  firstName: Steve
                  lastName: Hu
                  sinNumber: 123456789
                  status: open
                - num: 521999128
                  owner: stevehu
                  type: saving
                  firstName: Steve
                  lastName: Hu
                  sinNumber: 123456789
                  status: closed
    post:
      summary: Create an account
      operationId: createAccount
      requestBody:
        description: Open a new account
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Account'
      security:
        - account_auth:
            - 'account.w'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Null response
components:
  securitySchemes:
    account_auth:
      type: oauth2
      description: This API uses OAuth 2 with the client credential grant flow.
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          tokenUrl: 'https://localhost:6882/token'
          scopes:
            'account.w': update
            'account.r': query
  schemas:
    Account:
      type: object
      required:
        - num
        - name
        - type
        - firstName
        - lastName
        - sinNumber
        - status
      properties:
        num:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        sinNumber:
          type: string
        status:
          type: string
